CDL Investments sells Auckland property . CDL Investments on Wednesday said it had sold its Greenhithe , Auckland property for NZ $ 4 . 05 million , resulting in a profit of approximately $ 3 . 5 million . CDL said the profit was the result of a pending favourable zoning change . The sale , which follows the purchase of 68 hectares of land in Hamilton for $ 4 . 0 million , was a continuation of CDL ' s program of strategic acquisitions and the disposal of certain properties in a bid to reconfigure the company ' s property portfolio . " The company has made an early start in the construction season and is well placed to meet its budgeted development program for the 1997 financial year , " CDL said in a statement . - - Wellington Newsroom ( 64 4 ) 4734746 
